nus.sins2.device.reflectometer

Class ReflectometerStageDeviceParameters

  • java.lang.Object
    • nus.sins2.device.reflectometer.ReflectometerStageDeviceParameters

  • public final class ReflectometerStageDeviceParameters
extends java.lang.Object
    Reflectometer Stage Device parameter data.

    For local data storage of device parameter data.

    The controllers are indexed 0..2 (2 axes per controller) and the axes are indexed 0..5, where:
    axis 0 = maskX
    axis 1 = maskY
    axis 2 = maskZ
    axis 3 = detectorX
    axis 4 = maskT
    axis 5 = detectorT
